<SLUG> BC-HERBERT-COLUMN-1STLD-WRITETHRU-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COMMENTARY: SHADOW OF A HERO 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Subs 7th graf for updating) (Duplication warning: Also moved in `k' category) 
(JT) 
