<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: TECHNOLOGY FOR THE MASSES
 &HT;    Moving in (f) financial and (k) commentary categories for
release Sunday, Aug. 30.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
