<P>
   QUESO _ AUSTIN, Texas _ When Tom and Pam Stanley make queso,
they pump the peppers to it: jalapeno, habanero, chipotle,
fingerhot and serranos. Their Fiery Queso singes. Ah, but the heat
brought enough pleasure that five judges declared it the grand
prize winner of the Quest for Queso at the Texas Fiery Foods Show
recently at Palmer Auditorium. (Recipes included.) (Crider, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED.
