   RELIGION
</P>
<P>
   PREACHER-SWAP _ Treasure Coast Episcopal priest and an Anglican
parson from England swap jobs/homes/cars for the month of August.
(Gushee, Palm Beach Post) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
