<SLUG> BC-GORE-CLINTON-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GORE REITERATES HIS SUPPORT FOR HIS BOSS 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Recasts lede; pickup2ndgraf: During a)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By RACHEL GORDON  
 c.1998 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO _ Vice President Al Gore offered unqualified
