<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-27 14:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5406 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OUTDOORS-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      08-27 1685
