   SEPT. 25: Rosenthal/Baker
</P>
<P>
   SEPT. 26: Rich
</P>
<P>
   SEPT. 27: Herbert/Dowd
</P>
<P>
   SEPT..28: Safire
</P>
<P>
   SEPT. 29: Lewis &QL;
</P>
<P>
   SEPT. 30: Dowd/Rich
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
