<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-27 16:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5755 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RUSSIA-ECONOMY-0828-C     08-27 0812
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RUSSIA-ECONOMY-0828-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PRESSURE MOUNTS ON YELTSIN TO LEAVE AS RUBLE CONTINUES ITS
FREEFALL
 &HT;    With LATAM-ECONOMY-0828.
