</P>
<P>
   PANAMSAT-OUTLOOK (Cape Canaveral, Fla.) will not move in
tonight's New York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Aug. 27. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
