<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-27 19:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6111 &Cx1f; tab-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JUST-IN-TIME-(SENIOR-     08-27 0620
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JUST-IN-TIME-(SENIOR-MONTH)-ADVISORY-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; EDITORS: In recognition of Senior Month in September _ which
includes National Grandparents Day on the 13th _ The New York Times
Syndicate presents five stories of special interest to seniors.
</P>
