<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-27 19:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6151 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BONNIE-FLOODING-BOS &LR;      08-27 0888
