<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-27 20:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6216 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IRAQ-RITTER-BOS &LR;      08-27 1166
