 BC-ADD-BUDGET-AZR 
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients) 
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic editorial has been added for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for Friday, Aug. 28. If you
have any questions, please contact the Republic News Desk at (602)
271-8108.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
EDIT-FOREIGN-POLICY-DECEIT: The Clinton administration has
abandoned principle and candor in foreign policy, most recently in
regard to Iraq. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-08-27-98 2016EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
